<section id="About">
  <div>
    <p class="ram">Rammus Ma</p>
    <h1 id="title">About</h1>
  </div>
  <div id="img-div"> <img id="image" src="https://clps10160323.weebly.com/uploads/1/3/4/9/13492290/7656995_orig.jpg" alt="rammus ma"/>
    <figcaption id="img-caption">Rammus eating his favourite snack</figcaption></div>
    <p id="tribute-info">Rammus Ma is the cutest hamster in the world. His name is based on a character named "Rammus" from a famous video game-"League of Legends". He is now 1.5 years of age. He is a calm hamster as he can sit firmly on a palm and he seldom bites. He is also a clever hamster as he can easily discover hidden food. Rammus is a norturnal animal, so he usually rests during the day and is much more active during nighttime. Although he has poor eyesight as he does not need to rely on it, he has very strong sense of smell and hearing. He also has glands at his belly to scent-mark for navigation and setting territories.Rammus is a very interesting animal which makes him loved by many people.</p>
    <p>Learn more about hamsters, click <a id="tribute-link" target="_blank" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hamster">here</a></p>
  </div>  
