  <section id="takecare">
    <h2 class="tc">Taking care of him</h2>
    <p class="cage">Cage</p>
    <ul class="cagelist">
      <li>•	Use as big of a cage you can buy</li>
      <li>•	Spread paper bedding along the cage with more depth in winter and less in summer</li>
      <li>•	Essential items include a covered house, food bowl, water bottle and wheel</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="cage">Food</p>
    <ul class="cagelist">
      <li>•	Main food includes grains, seeds, dry vegetables and dry fruits</li>
      <li>•	Do not feed snacks such as peanuts and sunflower seeds too often</li>
      <li>•	He must drink boiled water</li>
    </ul>
    
